<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta name="description" content="Mariage de Marie et Robin" />
		<title>Marie & Robin - Mariage</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="layout">
			<header class="hero">
				<div class="hero-image-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
					<img src="/header-photo.png" alt="" class="hero-image" />
				</div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Mariage</p>
				<h1>Marie <span class="ampersand">&</span> Robin</h1>
				<p class="hero-date">Samedi 9 mai 2026</p>
			</header>

			<section class="panel intro">
				<p>
					Nous sommes heureux de vous inviter à célébrer notre mariage et de partager avec vous
					cette belle journée.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>Cérémonie religieuse</h2>
				<p class="lead">14 h 30 - Église Saint-Melaine</p>
				<p>Moëlan-sur-Mer</p>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>Reception</h2>
				<p class="lead">À partir de 17 h 30 - Manoir de Kerangosker</p>
				<p>Rue du Hénan, Kerangosker, 29930 Pont-Aven</p>
			</section>

			<section class="panel wide">
				<h2>Programme du samedi 9 mai</h2>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">14 h 30</span>
						<span class="event">Cérémonie à l'église</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">17 h 30</span>
						<span class="event">Cocktail au manoir</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">20 h 00</span>
						<span class="event">Diner</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="panel wide">
				<h2>Brunch du dimanche 10 mai</h2>
				<p class="lead">À partir de 11 h 00 - Manoir de Kerangosker</p>
				<p>Les festivités se prolongent le lendemain dans une ambiance plus décontractée.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>RSVP</h2>
				<p>Merci de nous répondre avant le <strong>1er mars 2026</strong>.</p>
				<p>Précisez le nombre de personnes, d'enfants et les régimes spéciaux.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>Contacts</h2>
				<p><strong>Marie :</strong> <a href="tel:+33618885425">06 18 88 54 25</a></p>
				<p><strong>Robin :</strong> <a href="tel:+33640254609">06 40 25 46 09</a></p>
				<p>
					<a href="mailto:mariebreuille@gmail.com">mariebreuille@gmail.com</a><br />
					<a href="mailto:robin4a4@gmail.com">robin4a4@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<footer class="footer">
				<p>Merci de célébrer cette journée avec nous.</p>
				<p class="signature">Marie & Robin</p>
			</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		--off-white: #f9f7f3;
		--off-white-dark: #ede9e0;
		--hydrangea: #7ba3c9;
		--hydrangea-light: #a8c5db;
		--green: #6b8e5a;
		--green-light: #8ba87a;
		--text: #3d3d3d;
		--text-light: #6b6b6b;
	}

	*,
	*::before,
	*::after {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	html {
		font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
		background: var(--off-white);
		color: var(--text);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(123, 163, 201, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(107, 142, 90, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
			var(--off-white);
	}

	.layout {
		max-width: 1020px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.hero {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.hero-image-wrap {
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 7;
		border: 1px solid rgba(61, 61, 61, 0.16);
		overflow: hidden;
		background: var(--off-white-dark);
	}

	.hero-image {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: 50% 58%;
		filter: saturate(0.95) contrast(0.98);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin-top: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	.signature {
		font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 500;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.ampersand {
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.hero-date {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: var(--green);
		letter-spacing: 0.03em;
	}

	.panel {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid rgba(61, 61, 61, 0.12);
		padding: 1.4rem 1.25rem;
	}

	.panel.wide,
	.intro {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.intro {
		background: transparent;
		border: 0;
		padding-top: 0.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.intro p {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
		font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
		font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 1.45rem);
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.65rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(123, 163, 201, 0.45);
	}

	p {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.panel p + p {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.lead {
		color: var(--text);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.timeline {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		border: 1px solid rgba(123, 163, 201, 0.25);
		padding: 0.75rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.1rem;
	}

	.time {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
	}

	.event {
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	a {
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		text-underline-offset: 0.15rem;
	}

	a:hover {
		color: var(--green);
	}

	.footer {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.signature {
		margin-top: 0.4rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.layout {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			padding-top: 1.25rem;
		}

		.hero-image-wrap {
			aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
		}
	}
</style>
